Dial H (000 - 015) (2012 - 2013) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire) 


A "Second Wave" title of DC's The New 52 initiative, featuring Nelson Jent, the latest bearer of the H Dial.

It was announced that Dial H will be cancelled with issue #15. DC also cancelled the series called Threshold at issue 8 both of the series where cancelled in August of 2013 due to low sales also marketing of the series.
